name: Monogram DLR
description:
Delarocca is a clothing mark just being born in Prague - the heart of Europe in a small
workshop where everything is hand-printed. Our t-shirts are mostly created by screen printing
technique, recenty we also use a poli-flex. Every t-shirt collection is a limited edition. A
motive is printed only 30 times globally and some are even printed only once for ever. This
guarantees 100% genuineness.

Men´s T-Shirt are made of 100% Cotton Material / Women´s T-Shirt are made of
combination of Cotton and Elasten.

Washing gently at 30 oC, do not iron over the image!
